input_str: Want a time tested recipe that includes a vegetable and formed into a popsicle? That's right, the combo exists and they're shockingly delicious. I've been making these Pea Pops for 8 years and to this day after a skeptical friend of Kenya and Chloe's tries it they end up falling in love. So much so that I've had a freezer full of different flavored popsicles and seen kids choose these over other sweet
